1
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:38,000
=Snow Fall=

2
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:40,650
=Snow Fall=
=Episode 19=

3
00:01:40,650 --> 00:01:41,940
(This drama is purely fictional.)

4
00:01:59,030 --> 00:02:00,080
It's too small.

5
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,640
I need a bigger space

6
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,280
and more personnel.

7
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:07,390
But Chi Shanying
has his eyes on us right now.

8
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:10,880
Those who dare to obstruct me shall die.

9
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:23,910
(Superintendent's Office)
Mu Lihua took my troops.

10
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:25,460
Now, she's not even picking up my calls.

11
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:27,600
Superintendent, take a look.

12
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:33,940
(Name list of deceased personnel)

13
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:37,550
Are they all dead?

14
00:02:37,790 --> 00:02:38,550
Yes, sir.

15
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:42,460
I think Miss Mu's training
is quite terrifying.

16
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,810
I couldn't see the training venue,

17
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,480
all of the troops she took were dead.

18
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:46,950
I found their bodies

19
00:02:46,950 --> 00:02:48,440
at several mass graves.

20
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:50,230
Go and find Mu Lihua.

21
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,360
Go and find Mu Lihua!

22
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,200
She has to give me an account for this!

23
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:54,790
Yes, sir.

24
00:02:56,530 --> 00:02:57,880
What kind of account do you want?

25
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:02,920
Miss Mu,

26
00:03:03,230 --> 00:03:04,480
you came uninvited, huh?

27
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:06,360
What's wrong?

28
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:08,710
Aren't you busy?

29
00:03:12,230 --> 00:03:14,230
I was planning
to talk to you about this.

30
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,490
Due to my carelessness,
some of your brothers

31
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:18,390
were burned to death some time ago.

32
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:20,910
However, I've told my assistant

33
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,420
to send them the compensation payment.

34
00:03:22,670 --> 00:03:23,480
Therefore,

35
00:03:23,950 --> 00:03:25,350
please send a few more men to me.

36
00:03:25,790 --> 00:03:27,070
You do make it sound easy.

37
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:29,040
You want a few more men?

38
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:31,160
You took my troops

39
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,040
without accomplishing my task.

40
00:03:33,390 --> 00:03:34,630
I would've shot you

41
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,350
if you were someone else!

42
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:40,790
Superintendent Chi,

43
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,720
I think you misunderstood something.

44
00:03:43,510 --> 00:03:45,000
Didn't I tell you before?

45
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,510
The Mu family will
definitely support you

46
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,760
as long as you keep supporting me.

47
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:54,320
Superintendent Chi,
you're the one going back on your word.

48
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,160
How could you blame me for this?

49
00:03:56,390 --> 00:03:59,390
When it comes to arguing,

50
00:03:59,830 --> 00:04:01,560
Miss Mu, you're truly something else.

51
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,600
You have a silver tongue.

52
00:04:05,350 --> 00:04:06,280
If that's the case,

53
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:08,200
I'll make myself clear.

54
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,790
All these brothers of mine

55
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,760
have been through
thick and thin with me.

56
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,910
They're strong and determined.

57
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,830
They can only die on the battlefield!

58
00:04:17,830 --> 00:04:19,730
Their names
shouldn't be appearing on this list!

59
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,590
If everyone knows

60
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,200
that I'd lost this many troops,

61
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,320
had the soldiers' morale shaken,

62
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,680
and had my tasks hindered

63
00:04:30,710 --> 00:04:32,000
because of you,

64
00:04:32,150 --> 00:04:34,630
I won't be able to give my brothers

65
00:04:34,710 --> 00:04:36,360
and the people

66
00:04:38,150 --> 00:04:39,680
an account.

67
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,470
Superintendent Chi,

68
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:46,920
you do live up to your title.

69
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:48,490
You do focus on the bigger picture.

70
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,320
I was being inconsiderate here.

71
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:53,470
Farewell.

72
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:11,290
Give it to me.

73
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,470
Mr. Shen,

74
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:49,030
Uncle Youwen called me just now and said

75
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,360
that Mr. Zhang had passed away.

76
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,270
You're here.

77
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:27,880
I'm back.

78
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,760
Has...

79
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,370
Has everything settled down?

80
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:32,880
Yes.

81
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:34,590
Good.

82
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,830
Mr. Shen,

83
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,320
this is the letter

84
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:56,200
Grandfather told me to hand it to you.

85
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,080
Don't worry.

86
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:02,590
You can leave
the Shen family's residence to me.

87
00:07:03,350 --> 00:07:04,640
I will do what

88
00:07:04,810 --> 00:07:06,150
Grandfather has done in the past.

89
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,760
As for your secret,

90
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:10,200
I will never tell
any strangers about it.

91
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,560
To me,

92
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,800
you never changed at all.

93
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:15,950
Thank you.

94
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:26,270
(Mr. Shen, please treat
this letter as our encounter.)

95
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,440
(As you saved me,)

96
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:30,640
(I guarded the tombs
for the Shen family.)

97
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:34,350
(I was lucky enough to live out
my years in peace and contentment.)

98
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:38,080
(I'm already content with my life.)

99
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:42,440
(You were always a considerate person.)

100
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,710
(I often think about this.)

101
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:47,120
(Although we knew
each other for 70 years,)

102
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,560
(we only met three to five times.)

103
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,910
(Now, I have to bid you
a hasty farewell.)

104
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:55,390
(I already have no regrets in life.)

105
00:07:56,710 --> 00:07:59,950
(As a general has his reputation
shattered one battle after another,)

106
00:08:00,710 --> 00:08:04,800
(he turns back
to look at the riverside,)

107
00:08:05,350 --> 00:08:08,120
(knowing that
his old friends are long gone.)

108
00:08:09,150 --> 00:08:13,560
(Now that we're parting ways,
I hope you can look after yourself.)

109
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:17,540
(To Mr. Shen)

110
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:24,150
It's my honor to make
your acquaintance as well.

111
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,350
So, do all of the other tablets

112
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:31,800
represent your family members?

113
00:08:32,530 --> 00:08:33,520
There are family members.

114
00:08:34,300 --> 00:08:35,350
There are friends as well.

115
00:08:36,230 --> 00:08:37,470
Will there be mine?

116
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:40,080
Not for now.

117
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,090
I will have one in the future, right?

118
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:45,950
All of these represent
my deceased family members and friends.

119
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:22,920
You're back.

120
00:09:23,350 --> 00:09:24,160
Yes, Miss Mu.

121
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:27,440
I was thinking that I should rush back
and clean the scene for you.

122
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,280
I never expected you
to clean it up already.

123
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:32,080
How was the investigation?

124
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:34,110
I did obtain some leads

125
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:35,820
when I did my investigation
in Suping Town.

126
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,400
(When my father was young,)

127
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:47,320
(he made acquaintance with a woman.)

128
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:49,230
(After that, she got pregnant.)

129
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,680
(She gave birth to a son.)

130
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,950
(Father brought her home.)

131
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:55,080
(I called her Madam Shen.)

132
00:09:55,210 --> 00:09:56,750
After that, Grandmother
found out

133
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:59,280
that she often killed chickens
and drank their blood at night.

134
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,870
Grandmother thought they were monsters.

135
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:04,470
When Father was away,

136
00:10:04,990 --> 00:10:06,750
she tied both her and her son up.

137
00:10:07,220 --> 00:10:08,490
She wanted to burn them to death.

138
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:10,590
Madam Shen?

139
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:11,710
That's right.

140
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,550
I have looked into
the Shen family genealogy.

141
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:15,040
That Madam Shen

142
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:16,110
was only known as Wei.

143
00:10:22,230 --> 00:10:23,870
(My ancestor once
mentioned in the diary)

144
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,590
(that the Mu family fought with
someone for the Blood Amber Stone.)

145
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:29,630
(That person was called Wei Qiu.)

146
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,630
(When she goes berserk,)

147
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:36,990
(she becomes super strong and swift.)

148
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:38,990
(She could rival 100 men)

149
00:10:39,990 --> 00:10:41,590
(with her fists alone.)

150
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:57,520
(The Mu family
suffered heavy casualties.)

151
00:10:58,870 --> 00:10:59,950
(Only my ancestor)

152
00:10:59,990 --> 00:11:01,280
(managed to escape frantically.)

153
00:11:01,630 --> 00:11:03,080
(He wrote this diary entry)

154
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,630
(with his remaining memories.)

155
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,560
In this diary, Wei Qiu's abilities

156
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:10,560
were the same as Shen Zhiheng's.

157
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:16,630
What do you think that proves?

158
00:11:17,470 --> 00:11:18,830
Could it be that this woman

159
00:11:18,830 --> 00:11:20,790
had handed the Blood Amber Stone
to Shen Zhiheng?

160
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:22,520
If that's the case,

161
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:25,590
that means

162
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:29,680
I have to get you at all costs.

163
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:32,560
Lin Zhen, we have to do something.

164
00:11:32,830 --> 00:11:34,710
We need to force him to show himself.

165
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:23,950
Who's there?

166
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:37,520
Let me do it.

167
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:38,800
Alright.

168
00:12:44,590 --> 00:12:45,520
What are you guys doing?

169
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:46,830
We're leaving Haidong.

170
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:49,950
Why are we leaving Haidong?

171
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,920
We're going to spend our days
in a peaceful place

172
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:53,830
when no one will pester
or cause trouble for us.

173
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:55,680
We're leaving Haidong, huh?

174
00:12:57,750 --> 00:13:00,230
But before that,
there's one more person to deal with.

175
00:13:02,470 --> 00:13:04,870
"Many people
have gone missing in Haidong."

176
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:07,560
"Practice caution
when you tread at night?"

177
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,790
That has nothing to do with me.

178
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:10,920
I didn't do it.

179
00:13:10,990 --> 00:13:12,320
I know it wasn't you.

180
00:13:12,710 --> 00:13:13,920
It should be Mu Lihua.

181
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:16,710
Chi Shanying has already lost

182
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:18,080
many of his guards.

183
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,990
They never came back
after heading to her place.

184
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:22,920
Even if the feud
of the Three Stones didn't exist,

185
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:25,230
we cannot allow Mu Lihua to remain here.

186
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,680
We need to deal with this threat
on Haidong's behalf.

187
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,110
What about Chi Shanying?

188
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:32,520
At least Chi Shanying is still a human.

189
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,350
But Mu Lihua

190
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:36,440
has already lost all sense of reason.

191
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,950
Fine. I'll follow your will.

192
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:41,440
But there's one thing
we need to discuss.

193
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:43,320
It's very important.

194
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,200
Is that all?

195
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:55,590
Yes.

196
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,080
Since this is

197
00:13:57,110 --> 00:13:58,350
so beneficial to you,

198
00:13:58,350 --> 00:13:59,750
you can do it yourself.

199
00:13:59,850 --> 00:14:01,230
You don't need to tell me about it.

200
00:14:01,710 --> 00:14:03,080
Don't tell me you think

201
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:05,520
that I'll cooperate with you
and surrender myself to him?

202
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,920
I didn't agree to
Li Yingliang's proposal for the benefits.

203
00:14:08,080 --> 00:14:09,040
I did it for your sake.

204
00:14:09,470 --> 00:14:10,520
For my sake?

205
00:14:11,990 --> 00:14:13,110
Please tell me the details.

206
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:14,990
You've offended the Haidong Army.

207
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:16,470
Chi Shanying won't let you off.

208
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:18,320
You also disclosed your immortality.

209
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,830
Mu Lihua won't let you off either.

210
00:14:19,860 --> 00:14:21,980
That's why I'm planning
to leave Haidong with you two.

211
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:23,420
Why do you still want to remain here?

212
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:24,920
Li Yingliang gave me his promise.

213
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,800
He said he could help us to leave

214
00:14:26,950 --> 00:14:28,520
as long as I helped him out.

215
00:14:28,830 --> 00:14:31,920
And, he even said that he would withdraw
from the relationship and help me

216
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,470
win Jingxue's heart.

217
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:36,990
Even if I agree,

218
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:39,520
Jin Jingxue won't agree to it.

219
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:41,830
We aren't machines.

220
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,400
We can't stop our feelings at will.

221
00:14:43,410 --> 00:14:44,950
We can't just change the person we love.

222
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:46,110
Even I could tell

223
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:47,560
that she loves Li Yingliang.

224
00:14:48,230 --> 00:14:49,440
Can't you tell?

225
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,830
I think Li Yingliang doesn't love
Jin Jingxue at all.

226
00:14:51,950 --> 00:14:53,950
How would you know that?

227
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:55,800
If he loved Jin Jingxue,

228
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,950
he wouldn't use her
as his bargaining chip.

229
00:14:58,230 --> 00:15:00,320
If I were him,
I would never be able to do that.

230
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,520
Strange.

231
00:15:04,710 --> 00:15:06,400
How did an innocent guy like you

232
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:08,110
actually hide this from me
for three years?

233
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:11,280
Heng, just take it
as if you're fulfilling my wish.

234
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,750
This is beneficial to you as well.

235
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:13,800
Brothers are stand-in fathers.

236
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,390
In the future,
I'll treat you like my father.

237
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,270
I'll be filial to you.

238
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,470
And, I can't rest at ease

239
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:18,620
when Jingxue is in Haidong.

240
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:20,800
I must've owed you a lot
in my past life, huh?

241
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,320
Heng, you're the best.

242
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:24,590
I can cooperate with you.

243
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:25,920
But I have one request.

244
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,950
I need to see Mu Lihua at the very end.

245
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,470
Only then will I leave.

246
00:15:36,310 --> 00:15:37,350
Why are you looking for me?

247
00:15:37,950 --> 00:15:38,870
Am I great?

248
00:15:39,180 --> 00:15:40,750
You're much more interesting
than Heng.

249
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:41,560
You're just like me.

250
00:15:41,830 --> 00:15:43,440
Am I great or not?

251
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:46,750
You're swift and strong.

252
00:15:47,400 --> 00:15:48,080
Yeah, you are.

253
00:15:50,630 --> 00:15:53,400
If so, can I do anything
to help you guys out?

254
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:54,440
In what?

255
00:15:55,950 --> 00:15:58,710
Chi Shanying and Mu Lihua
are powerful as well, right?

256
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,350
If so,

257
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,440
let's get rid of them in secret.

258
00:16:09,630 --> 00:16:11,080
I cannot kill.

259
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,320
It's fine.

260
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:13,870
Both of them are bad eggs.

261
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:15,520
Let's get rid of them in secret.

262
00:16:15,530 --> 00:16:16,530
Don't tell Heng about it.

263
00:16:17,700 --> 00:16:19,110
What were you two whispering about?

264
00:16:20,470 --> 00:16:21,460
Didn't you have business?

265
00:16:25,590 --> 00:16:26,400
You, come with me.

266
00:16:29,100 --> 00:16:31,390
(Third, don't reveal your true form)
You broke the third rule today.

267
00:16:31,520 --> 00:16:32,870
Weilian isn't a stranger.

268
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:34,590
You're talking back to me, huh?

269
00:16:35,950 --> 00:16:36,750
Good.

270
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:41,710
Copy the Six Rules 30 times.

271
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:43,800
You can only sleep after that.

272
00:16:46,040 --> 00:16:47,040
30 times isn't enough?

273
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:49,040
Copy it 40 times, then.

274
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:56,620
You're not allowed to sleep
until you're done.

275
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:09,800
Little crow,

276
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:10,830
I'll take you outside.

277
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,180
But don't make a sound, okay?

278
00:17:12,390 --> 00:17:13,720
If not, I'll pluck your feather.

279
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:15,830
Let's go.

280
00:17:47,430 --> 00:17:48,110
What's going on?

281
00:17:56,520 --> 00:17:58,520
Why were you terrified by a stupid crow?

282
00:17:58,560 --> 00:17:59,870
You can just chase it away.

283
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:09,830
Go away!

284
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:11,320
Go away!

285
00:18:15,150 --> 00:18:15,630
What a fool.

286
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,190
Scram!

287
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:19,560
Useless fool.

288
00:18:35,870 --> 00:18:37,280
Go away!

289
00:18:39,870 --> 00:18:41,590
Go away!

290
00:19:10,910 --> 00:19:12,320
There's a ghost!

291
00:19:24,110 --> 00:19:25,000
What ghost?

292
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,040
How could there be a ghost?

293
00:19:29,760 --> 00:19:30,560
Come out!

294
00:19:32,150 --> 00:19:33,590
Stop hiding!

295
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:34,520
Show yourself!

296
00:19:53,190 --> 00:19:54,040
Where is he?

297
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:56,430
Show yourself!

298
00:19:56,670 --> 00:19:57,800
Are you sick in the head?

299
00:20:00,150 --> 00:20:01,870
Isn't it tiring
to swing around like that?

300
00:20:01,910 --> 00:20:03,280
Show yourself if you dare!

301
00:20:08,190 --> 00:20:09,590
What are you looking at? Look at me!

302
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,290
Investigate this case tomorrow.

303
00:20:12,390 --> 00:20:14,720
Find him at all costs!

304
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:15,350
Yes, sir.

305
00:20:57,300 --> 00:20:59,980
If I could scare you enough to leave
Haidong by taking this bullet,

306
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:00,910
that'll be worth it.

307
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:11,150
Sorry about that.

308
00:21:11,190 --> 00:21:12,560
I plucked one of your feathers.

309
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:13,800
Eat up. Here.

310
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:18,350
Why are you like this?

311
00:21:18,350 --> 00:21:19,110
You're so petty.

312
00:21:19,150 --> 00:21:20,590
It's just one feather.

313
00:21:20,910 --> 00:21:21,590
You are too much.

314
00:21:21,630 --> 00:21:22,840
I won't be friends with you!

315
00:21:26,630 --> 00:21:27,320
Mi Lan.

316
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:32,630
Mr. Shen.

317
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,430
You woke up early today, huh?

318
00:21:39,910 --> 00:21:40,910
I couldn't sleep.

319
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:44,040
Go and get changed.
Let's go and admire some views.

320
00:21:44,670 --> 00:21:45,190
Alright.

321
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:55,960
Say,

322
00:21:58,830 --> 00:22:00,040
he only tried to terrify me.

323
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:02,350
He didn't harm me.

324
00:22:04,320 --> 00:22:05,150
What was his goal?

325
00:22:05,410 --> 00:22:07,430
Superintendent Chi,
judging from your description,

326
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:09,520
he appeared out of nowhere
and was extremely swift.

327
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,380
I'm sure it's not an ordinary person.

328
00:22:11,910 --> 00:22:12,880
Could it be Shen Zhiheng?

329
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:14,080
That's impossible.

330
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:17,430
He has a small figure.
It's not Shen Zhiheng.

331
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:18,830
A small figure...

332
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:21,720
Could it be Mu Lihua?

333
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:22,760
I have a report.

334
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:24,390
Come in.

335
00:22:29,110 --> 00:22:31,040
Superintendent Chi,
someone named Situ Weilian

336
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:32,070
is waiting for you outside.

337
00:22:32,080 --> 00:22:33,720
He said he has news of Li Yingliang.

338
00:22:42,390 --> 00:22:44,320
Why didn't Li Yingliang
come here himself?

339
00:22:45,830 --> 00:22:47,910
He said he didn't dare
to show himself in public yet.

340
00:22:48,320 --> 00:22:49,190
He also said

341
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:51,520
that he didn't hand the documents
to Shen Zhiheng.

342
00:22:51,590 --> 00:22:53,000
Shen Zhiheng stole them.

343
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:55,110
Shen Zhiheng wanted to frame him.

344
00:22:55,280 --> 00:22:56,430
He wanted to use you

345
00:22:56,630 --> 00:22:57,760
to get rid of him.

346
00:22:59,830 --> 00:23:01,430
If so, aren't you afraid

347
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:03,110
that I'll doubt your words

348
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:04,430
and kill you instead?

349
00:23:04,830 --> 00:23:06,630
I've never thought of that.

350
00:23:07,870 --> 00:23:08,800
Would you though?

351
00:23:10,000 --> 00:23:10,960
Such audacity.

352
00:23:11,300 --> 00:23:12,430
How dare you speak like that?

353
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:25,110
Actually, he told me to come here

354
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,870
so that you could go there
and visit him.

355
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:29,110
He said he didn't believe in anyone else

356
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:29,910
except for you.

357
00:23:33,320 --> 00:23:34,080
Fine.

358
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:38,760
Please tell Li Yingliang

359
00:23:38,800 --> 00:23:40,280
that I'll visit him.

360
00:23:40,670 --> 00:23:41,480
Got it.

361
00:23:41,810 --> 00:23:42,970
Farewell, Superintendent Chi.

362
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:51,720
By the way, I almost forgot about
the most important part.

363
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:53,110
Li Yingliang also said

364
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:54,910
that he would show his loyalty

365
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,000
by coming up with a way

366
00:23:56,190 --> 00:23:57,480
to help you capture Shen Zhiheng.

367
00:24:00,830 --> 00:24:03,480
Did Li Yingliang
tell you about it, then?

368
00:24:06,190 --> 00:24:07,280
I'm just a messenger.

369
00:24:07,290 --> 00:24:08,000
I'll be going now.

370
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:14,320
This Li Yingliang

371
00:24:15,040 --> 00:24:16,670
is truly dumb.

372
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:19,040
I was looking for him all this while
but to no avail.

373
00:24:19,190 --> 00:24:21,630
Now, he actually
sought help from his enemy.

374
00:24:22,110 --> 00:24:23,560
He even told Situ Weilian

375
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:24,910
about his plan.

376
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:28,000
Situ Weilian is on Shen Zhiheng's side.

377
00:24:28,190 --> 00:24:29,720
If Situ Weilian knows about his plan,

378
00:24:29,760 --> 00:24:31,390
Shen Zhiheng will know about it too.

379
00:24:32,390 --> 00:24:34,280
So, Superintendent Chi,
what's your plan?

380
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,800
In my opinion,

381
00:24:36,870 --> 00:24:37,800
maybe

382
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:40,870
Shen Zhiheng was the one
who came up with this plan.

383
00:24:41,150 --> 00:24:43,150
Maybe the three of them are in cahoots.

384
00:24:43,150 --> 00:24:44,670
They're staging an act for me to see.

385
00:24:45,410 --> 00:24:48,290
Superintendent Chi, I'll take my men
to the Jin Mansion and arrest him.

386
00:24:49,190 --> 00:24:49,870
No need for that.

387
00:24:50,830 --> 00:24:52,910
Superintendent Chi,
do you intend to see him, then?

388
00:24:54,390 --> 00:24:55,110
Yes.

389
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:57,190
Of course.

390
00:24:57,560 --> 00:24:59,110
He spent so much effort

391
00:24:59,110 --> 00:25:00,390
to come up with this plan.

392
00:25:00,390 --> 00:25:01,670
I want to see what he's up to.

393
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:02,950
I'll arrange for it immediately.

394
00:25:07,390 --> 00:25:08,390
Mr. Shen,

395
00:25:09,280 --> 00:25:10,630
I didn't sleep last night.

396
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:11,760
You didn't sleep?

397
00:25:12,630 --> 00:25:13,480
What did you do, then?

398
00:25:14,280 --> 00:25:15,520
I went to scare Chi Shanying.

399
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:16,860
Scare?

400
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,860
Wasn't that what you did

401
00:25:19,860 --> 00:25:21,060
to chase my mother away?

402
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,240
You said I mustn't kill.

403
00:25:23,250 --> 00:25:24,530
I can at least scare them, right?

404
00:25:28,760 --> 00:25:31,350
Did I do something wrong again?

405
00:25:32,430 --> 00:25:33,390
That's not it.

406
00:25:33,590 --> 00:25:34,830
That's pretty good.

407
00:25:35,520 --> 00:25:37,080
But you must take note
of your safety.

408
00:25:38,230 --> 00:25:40,080
You must form a plan
before you deal with foes.

409
00:25:40,090 --> 00:25:41,990
You shouldn't act
on your own initiative like this.

410
00:25:42,430 --> 00:25:44,190
What if you alert them to your presence?

411
00:25:45,080 --> 00:25:45,870
Will I?

412
00:25:46,670 --> 00:25:48,400
Chi Shanying is stationed in Haidong.

413
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:49,920
He's in a position

414
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:51,480
where his moves will affect everything.

415
00:25:52,080 --> 00:25:54,520
At least he and Mu Lihua
can restrain each other.

416
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:57,630
What should we do
if you do scare him away?

417
00:25:58,830 --> 00:26:00,560
I guess he's stronger than my mother.

418
00:26:00,700 --> 00:26:03,210
He doesn't run away
for the first time.

419
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,190
You're right.

420
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:06,080
He won't run away just from that.

421
00:26:06,430 --> 00:26:08,190
He can't bear
to part with his position.

422
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:14,150
I've lived for over 100 years.

423
00:26:15,110 --> 00:26:16,240
For the past 100 years,

424
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:18,430
initially, I was uncertain of my future.

425
00:26:18,630 --> 00:26:20,190
Then I gradually stabilized my life.

426
00:26:20,630 --> 00:26:21,910
And life became interesting.

427
00:26:22,910 --> 00:26:23,870
And now,

428
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:26,390
I live as if I'm a zombie.

429
00:26:27,110 --> 00:26:29,390
Even so, I still chose
to become a decent human.

430
00:26:31,150 --> 00:26:33,150
I thrived as a human.

431
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:36,000
Even so, I still don't understand
the meaning of being human.

432
00:26:36,520 --> 00:26:38,590
Mr. Shen, I didn't feel like living

433
00:26:40,350 --> 00:26:41,590
before I met you.

434
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:46,390
But now, I wish to live.

435
00:26:47,760 --> 00:26:48,590
Me too.

436
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:49,720
Mi Lan,

437
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:54,000
let's act together next time, okay?

438
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:55,280
Okay.

439
00:27:00,390 --> 00:27:02,350
I don't know when it'll stop snowing,

440
00:27:02,810 --> 00:27:04,600
but I'm already
looking forward to the days

441
00:27:04,670 --> 00:27:06,800
when we can listen to the rain together.

442
00:27:08,210 --> 00:27:09,520
Mr. Shen, I'm also looking forward

443
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:12,350
to every single day
I'll be spending with you.

444
00:27:37,190 --> 00:27:38,000
Liang.

445
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:43,670
Thank you, Miss Jin.

446
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:46,000
What's on your mind?

447
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:48,520
As long as my plan proceeds smoothly,

448
00:27:49,190 --> 00:27:51,190
I can return to my position.

449
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:54,240
Shen Zhiheng and
Situ Weilian will be fine.

450
00:27:54,430 --> 00:27:55,560
Miss Jin, don't worry.

451
00:27:56,630 --> 00:27:57,870
I won't harm them.

452
00:27:57,870 --> 00:27:59,580
I won't treat them
as my foes in the future.

453
00:27:59,590 --> 00:28:01,430
Chi Shanying has held Guisheng captive.

454
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:03,040
I have to rescue him.

455
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:41,150
Superintendent Chi.

456
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:01,590
Superintendent Chi.

457
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:16,560
Li Yingliang.

458
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:22,390
You do know
that I can kill you directly, right?

459
00:29:23,250 --> 00:29:24,870
Superintendent Chi,
I never betrayed you.

460
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:26,860
Shen Zhiheng captured me
to his warehouse.

461
00:29:26,870 --> 00:29:28,280
He almost tortured me to death.

462
00:29:28,290 --> 00:29:30,080
I only managed to escape
by digging a hole.

463
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:32,660
I didn't even dare
to walk on the streets after my escape.

464
00:29:32,670 --> 00:29:34,040
I'm afraid that
he might capture me again.

465
00:29:34,050 --> 00:29:35,390
So I'm hiding
in the Jin Mansion.

466
00:29:35,870 --> 00:29:37,890
I thought of a perfect plan
to kill Shen Zhiheng.

467
00:29:37,990 --> 00:29:40,470
That's why I risked my life
and sent someone to look for you.

468
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,950
Do you think no one else except for you

469
00:29:42,950 --> 00:29:45,600
can complete this task for me?

470
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:48,470
Have you ever considered this?

471
00:29:48,600 --> 00:29:49,550
Ever since

472
00:29:49,550 --> 00:29:51,030
you took over Shen Zhiheng's case,

473
00:29:51,120 --> 00:29:53,440
you never accomplished anything!

474
00:29:53,790 --> 00:29:56,030
Even Mu Lihua's ring is
much stronger than you!

475
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:57,370
It's much more stronger than you.

476
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:59,710
Superintendent Chi, I'm different.

477
00:29:59,950 --> 00:30:00,790
I'm more loyal to you

478
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:01,990
than anyone else.

479
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:18,030
Do you know

480
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:20,790
what I did before I became a soldier?

481
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,640
I don't know.

482
00:30:22,950 --> 00:30:24,360
Before I became a soldier,

483
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:27,470
I was a mentee

484
00:30:28,230 --> 00:30:29,470
in a barber shop.

485
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:33,270
My first job

486
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:35,120
was to help an officer
shave his mustache.

487
00:30:35,310 --> 00:30:36,360
Back then,

488
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:38,710
I was new.

489
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:40,510
I was nervous.

490
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:42,950
My hand was shaky.

491
00:30:42,950 --> 00:30:44,400
I cut

492
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,750
the officer's face.

493
00:30:45,790 --> 00:30:46,840
He was bleeding.

494
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:50,230
All those soldiers were pointing
their guns at me and my mentor.

495
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:51,840
I thought I was done for.

496
00:30:52,990 --> 00:30:54,600
I thought I was dead for sure.

497
00:30:56,160 --> 00:30:57,470
But I didn't expect

498
00:30:58,200 --> 00:31:00,080
that the officer
didn't utter a single word.

499
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:01,950
He left after that.

500
00:31:05,120 --> 00:31:06,160
Those days,

501
00:31:06,840 --> 00:31:08,920
I was leading an uneasy life.

502
00:31:10,950 --> 00:31:11,950
After half a month,

503
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,950
that officer came back.

504
00:31:15,340 --> 00:31:17,600
This time, he didn't bring
any soldiers or guns with him.

505
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,680
He came alone.

506
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:22,160
He designated me to shave his mustache.

507
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:26,230
He said he believed that I didn't do it
on purpose the first time around.

508
00:31:26,470 --> 00:31:29,080
He believed that I wouldn't
repeat my mistake.

509
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:30,840
Li Yingliang,

510
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:33,550
you've messed up so many times.

511
00:31:33,550 --> 00:31:35,200
You've gotten yourself
into plenty of trouble.

512
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:37,270
I never punished you severely

513
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:40,160
because I took your past merit
into consideration.

514
00:31:40,230 --> 00:31:42,230
I still trusted you.

515
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:44,400
That's why I'm willing
to give you another chance.

516
00:31:45,270 --> 00:31:46,120
Trust

517
00:31:46,950 --> 00:31:48,400
is very important.

518
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,400
You shouldn't let me down.

519
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:53,190
Superintendent Chi,
I won't let you down.

520
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:55,750
I'll definitely make it
as long as you give me one more chance.

521
00:31:59,270 --> 00:31:59,920
Have a seat.

522
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,950
Tell me about your plan.

523
00:32:05,990 --> 00:32:07,920
This time, we'll outsmart him.

524
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,710
We'll make
Shen Zhiheng sign a confession.

525
00:32:10,710 --> 00:32:12,020
We'll announce it in the newspaper

526
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:15,360
that the firm was disclosing the Haidong
Army's confidential documents, not me.

527
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:17,510
I believe that I can accomplish this task

528
00:32:17,510 --> 00:32:19,400
with the help of
Li Guisheng and Situ Weilian.

529
00:32:20,310 --> 00:32:21,950
Not Li Guisheng.

530
00:32:23,300 --> 00:32:24,360
The people demanded me

531
00:32:24,360 --> 00:32:25,790
to give them an account.

532
00:32:25,840 --> 00:32:27,680
I have no choice
but to lock Li Guisheng up.

533
00:32:30,360 --> 00:32:32,190
Superintendent Chi,
you're considerate indeed.

534
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:35,510
Superintendent Chi, if my plan does work out,

535
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:38,790
can you please let Li Guisheng go?

536
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:40,640
What about Mu Lihua?

537
00:32:42,360 --> 00:32:43,950
Why didn't you mention her?

538
00:32:44,230 --> 00:32:45,880
Mu Lihua did capture

539
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,470
Shen Zhiheng before this.

540
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:50,920
Superintendent Chi,
pardon me for being frank,

541
00:32:51,470 --> 00:32:53,080
but Mu Lihua is not trustworthy.

542
00:32:53,540 --> 00:32:54,710
Didn't you realize something?

543
00:32:55,030 --> 00:32:57,360
Haidong had been in turmoil
ever since she came here.

544
00:32:57,540 --> 00:32:59,160
And, plenty of people have gone missing.

545
00:32:59,580 --> 00:33:01,470
Why couldn't that
be the work of Shen Zhiheng?

546
00:33:01,550 --> 00:33:03,680
He could've gone berserk
and killed all of them.

547
00:33:03,990 --> 00:33:05,550
Shen Zhiheng has a sense of decency.

548
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:07,190
He wasn't willing
to get death-row convicts.

549
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,640
Why would he lose his mind

550
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:09,640
and attack the people?

551
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:12,200
You see,

552
00:33:13,360 --> 00:33:14,640
Mu Lihua gets her way

553
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:15,600
at all costs.

554
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:17,160
(Many missing in Haidong)
She only cares about her own interests.

555
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,710
She never respects life.

556
00:33:20,270 --> 00:33:22,680
Superintendent Chi,
you mustn't trust her.

557
00:33:30,360 --> 00:33:31,920
We can proceed with your plan.

558
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:33,510
But Li Yingliang,

559
00:33:33,990 --> 00:33:35,200
trust

560
00:33:36,310 --> 00:33:37,600
is very important.

561
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:40,080
You mustn't let me down.

562
00:33:40,510 --> 00:33:42,270
Yes, I understand.

563
00:33:42,750 --> 00:33:44,440
Thank you, Superintendent Chi.

564
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:45,990
Get me a new pot of tea.

565
00:33:46,360 --> 00:33:48,120
The tea you poured for me was cold.

566
00:33:48,840 --> 00:33:49,470
Yes, sir.

567
00:34:52,350 --> 00:34:53,560
Why are you still awake?

568
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:07,520
You don't need to overreact.

569
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:09,750
As if I was trying to hit you.

570
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:23,370
I'll repay your kindness
once I make a comeback.

571
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:27,910
How do you intend to repay me?

572
00:35:31,430 --> 00:35:32,710
I'll buy you expensive dowries.

573
00:35:35,910 --> 00:35:37,120
Who cares about that?

574
00:35:39,230 --> 00:35:40,830
I don't even have a fiance.

575
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:43,910
Who knows when I'll be able
to use the dowries you buy?

576
00:35:44,640 --> 00:35:46,000
Now, you're saying all this.

577
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:48,110
What if you go back on your word
in the future?

578
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:51,270
I think Situ Weilian is a worthy groom.

579
00:35:55,080 --> 00:35:56,350
Who do you think you are?

580
00:35:58,500 --> 00:35:59,880
Now, you're making the call for me?

581
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:01,790
You don't like him?

582
00:36:02,430 --> 00:36:03,600
I don't.

583
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:06,430
I think he's nice to you.

584
00:36:06,910 --> 00:36:08,120
You're nice to him too.

585
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:11,750
Does that mean I need to marry him?

586
00:36:26,790 --> 00:36:28,870
Li Yingliang, I'm ever nicer to you.

587
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:36,680
I'm sleepy.

588
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:37,870
Rest early.

589
00:36:38,420 --> 00:36:41,300
♪Since I dwelled in this world♪

590
00:36:45,830 --> 00:36:47,560
I told you to stay away from me.

591
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:49,910
I won't.

592
00:36:51,620 --> 00:36:54,220
♪Unable to feel♪

593
00:36:54,660 --> 00:37:00,140
♪The hot tears of my soul♪

594
00:37:01,810 --> 00:37:02,830
Have you lost your mind?

595
00:37:04,830 --> 00:37:05,960
That's right.

596
00:37:07,540 --> 00:37:13,300
♪It delivers savage blows to my heart
and condemns my helplessness♪

597
00:37:13,540 --> 00:37:19,900
♪It wraps around my inner demon
like a nightmare♪

598
00:37:20,100 --> 00:37:26,020
♪Relentlessly chasing and thirsting
for blood without remorse♪

599
00:37:27,340 --> 00:37:27,920
Whatever.

600
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:32,860
♪Shouting alone in the bustling crowd♪

601
00:37:32,940 --> 00:37:34,580
♪The scorching sun burns me♪

602
00:37:34,660 --> 00:37:39,140
♪Leaving me restless and agitated♪

603
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:45,300
♪That long-thirsty
heart beats once more♪

604
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:52,300
♪The blazing flames burn me,
leaving me in a wretched state♪

605
00:37:52,820 --> 00:37:58,340
♪Along this road with no place to flee♪

606
00:37:58,420 --> 00:38:04,700
♪I can once again see
the blood-dripping flowers bloom♪

607
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:11,060
♪That was also the passionate grandeur
I longed for♪

608
00:38:11,220 --> 00:38:14,140
♪The light of desire♪

609
