to make a living with me.

616
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:44,390
You get whatever you desire.

617
00:38:44,830 --> 00:38:46,230
Why must you be together with me?

618
00:38:46,710 --> 00:38:47,790
I get whatever I desire.

619
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:50,040
That's why I can be together
with anyone I like.

620
00:38:51,520 --> 00:38:52,680
I'll sell you off tomorrow.

621
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:53,750
I'll show you who I am.

622
00:38:54,080 --> 00:38:54,640
Fine.

623
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:57,270
You have to find someone good-looking.

624
00:38:57,830 --> 00:38:58,960
I won't take any ugly men.

625
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:18,600
I'll be leaving tomorrow.

626
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:28,040
Is it that urgent?

627
00:39:28,950 --> 00:39:30,580
I have to resolve it
as soon as possible.

628
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:32,230
Even if I'll lose my future,

629
00:39:33,230 --> 00:39:35,080
I have to clear my name

630
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:36,350
and save myself.

631
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:38,750
If this keeps up,

632
00:39:39,790 --> 00:39:41,000
you'll be implicated too.

633
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:42,230
I'm not afraid of that.

634
00:39:46,270 --> 00:39:48,160
Don't worry. I won't be in danger.

635
00:39:51,830 --> 00:39:53,710
I'll come back
once I've resolved the issue.

636
00:39:56,950 --> 00:39:58,910
You don't need to coax me
with your sweet words.

637
00:39:59,390 --> 00:40:02,080
I never intended for you
to be responsible for me.

638
00:40:02,750 --> 00:40:04,830
I might not even agree
even if you want to marry me.

639
00:40:06,830 --> 00:40:09,520
I'm serious. I'm not trying to coax you.

640
00:40:09,710 --> 00:40:11,160
I've never coaxed you before this.

641
00:40:15,390 --> 00:40:16,560
You just don't want to.

642
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:45,270
Anyway, just wait for me.

643
00:40:47,270 --> 00:40:48,270
Wait for my return.

644
00:40:52,870 --> 00:40:54,350
If so, I'll trust you this time.

645
00:40:55,580 --> 00:40:57,870
But don't think that I'm using this
to threaten you here.

646
00:40:58,270 --> 00:40:59,520
If so,

647
00:40:59,640 --> 00:41:00,790
you'll be belittling me.

648
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:21,960
Dumplings. Eat up.

649
00:44:07,480 --> 00:44:08,560
Liang,

650
00:44:11,040 --> 00:44:12,390
