651
00:44:23,389 --> 00:44:25,889
♪Like the care poured by the moonlight♪

652
00:44:26,059 --> 00:44:28,969
♪Your inadvertent touch♪

653
00:44:30,769 --> 00:44:36,189
♪This extraordinary shell
wraps loneliness♪

654
00:44:38,259 --> 00:44:43,869
♪If I can no longer see your silhouette♪

655
00:44:44,349 --> 00:44:46,209
♪I would trade my lifetime♪

656
